dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text: GEE, IF YOU'RE THE RULER OF “HECK” YOU MUST HAVE SOME KIND OF AWESOME NAME.

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text:
WELL, WHAT IS IT?
SOMETHING LIKE
“KING OF EVIL” OR
“LORD OF DARKNESS”?

dialogue.speaker: Dogbert
dialogue.text:
YOU CAN CALL ME
PHIL, PRINCE OF
INSUFFICIENT LIGHT.
